lead_paragraph: Chris Sale took a shutout into the sixth inning, Brett Lawrie homered for the third straight day and the Chicago White Sox beat the Baltimore Orioles 7-1 Sunday for a split of the four-game series.

headline.print_headline: Sale Stays Unbeaten as White Sox Beat Orioles 7-1 for Split
